title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“...wild and wooly snap-front yolk-shouldered shirts are showing up under $300 sports jackets.”—Playboy, July, 1980. [Submitted by Dennis Moore, Greenville, South Carolina, who comments, The yoke's on y'all, boys.]
